h2. Required Browsers

All tests should be run from the following browser/OS combinations to ensure ODE works for a wide audience.

|Browser   | Windows  | OS X  | Linux |
|Chrome   |    X           |  X     |   X      |
|Firefox    |    X           |  X     |   X      |
|Safari      |                 |  X     |           |
|IE            |    X           |         |           |

